narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: I learned how to form a syllabus and how to figure out which sources are important. I learned a lot from one on one conversations with my professor. We met often and engaged in the text as well as about larger concepts.

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: I can only name strengths. The professor was accessible and met with me often. He often provided guidance on what to read and was very engaged in our conversations.

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: Yes i highly recommend doing an independent study with a professor. You learn not only about your subject but also about how to study history.
